y of the votes cast (assuming there was a quorum), but another proposal =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0to amend Churchill=E2=80=99s corporate charter to stop being a =
SPAC and to allow the issuance of shares in the transaction =E2=80=94=C2=A0=
was a prerequisite to doing the merger and required a majority of the share=
